relatedItem.note: PROJECT FOR A HOUSE FOR Mme. LA COMTESSE DU BARRY (1768-69): Architect LE DOUX. The Theatre in this project of 1768-69 should be compared with that built by Le Doux for La Guimard 1772 on a piece of this ground along the Chaussèe d'Antin. Compare also with the Private Teatro of Cardinal Ottoboni built by Juvarra some seventy years earlier in Roma, about 1705. (See Plate 2. The Mask, January. 7925)
